Deprecated API

Contents

  • Classes
  • Methods
  • Classes 
    Class Description
    brave.grpc.GrpcClientParser
    Since 5.12 use RpcTracing.clientRequestParser() or RpcTracing.clientResponseParser().
    brave.grpc.GrpcParser
    Since 5.12 use parsers in RpcTracing.
    brave.grpc.GrpcServerParser
    Since 5.12 use RpcTracing.serverRequestParser() or RpcTracing.serverResponseParser().
  • Methods 
    Method Description
    brave.grpc.GrpcClientParser.onMessageReceived​(M, SpanCustomizer)
    Since 5.12 use ClientCall.Listener.onMessage(Object).
    brave.grpc.GrpcClientParser.onMessageSent​(M, SpanCustomizer)
    Since 5.12 use ClientCall.sendMessage(Object).
    brave.grpc.GrpcParser.errorParser()
    This is only used in Zipkin reporting. Since 5.12, use ZipkinSpanHandler.Builder.errorTag(Tag)
    brave.grpc.GrpcServerParser.onMessageReceived​(M, SpanCustomizer)
    Since 5.12 use ServerCall.sendMessage(Object).
    brave.grpc.GrpcServerParser.onMessageSent​(M, SpanCustomizer)
    Since 5.12 use ServerCall.Listener.onMessage(Object).
    brave.grpc.GrpcTracing.Builder.clientParser​(GrpcClientParser)
    Since 5.12 use RpcTracing.Builder.clientRequestParser(RpcRequestParser) or RpcTracing.Builder.clientResponseParser(RpcResponseParser).
    brave.grpc.GrpcTracing.Builder.grpcPropagationFormatEnabled​(boolean)
    The only user of this format was Census, which was removed from gRPC in version v1.27.
    brave.grpc.GrpcTracing.Builder.serverParser​(GrpcServerParser)
    Since 5.12 use RpcTracing.Builder.serverRequestParser(RpcRequestParser) or RpcTracing.Builder.serverResponseParser(RpcResponseParser).
